{
  "stem": "1419.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Any time I look at the book-- [LAUGHS] funny thing, I'm just looking all these-- all these pages that say about Stalingrad, where they got defeated.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Any place the Germans get defeated, that's my pleasure to read [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when they get defeated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Any, any place they had success, I don't care too much about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But any place that they-- any chapter that I can see defeated, where they got, you know, thrown out from certain countries, defeated in something, that's my pleasure to read it today.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's the history.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't know if they didn't care, the world   didn't care.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that we-- we knew that England and, and, and Russia [INAUDIBLE] fighting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were left on, on our own.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody was fighting for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody's, nobody's doing anything about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know nothing, nothing about what, what, what would happen to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have no hope.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had-- we were hoping that the war going to end and we were going to survive, but we didn't see-- we didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't see it there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, sometimes I, I, I, I think about it, how we really survived, the small things how I went through, how I survived.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I want to tell you about in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Being in Plaszow, I was lucky to work in the-- in the places, what they call the [GERMAN] that we, we put up barracks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were-- we were-- we could-- we could go from place to place, in a way, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
